title: Cafe del Soul
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Organic, Juice bar, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic and mostly vegetarian with chicken being the only meat offered. Menu features wraps, salads, rice bowls, fresh juices, smoothies, and desserts vary from vegan cookies and cupcakes to raw chocolate truffles, ginger candy, and coconut macaroons. Most dishes can be made vegan upon request. Free Wi-Fi.
